## Editing add-ons

**Change details:** Update names, descriptions, photos, and pricing anytime
**Modify conditions:** Adjust availability rules as your business needs change
**Update categories:** Move add-ons between categories or create new ones

## Managing availability 

**Out of stock:** Mark add-ons unavailable when items run out
**Seasonal updates:** Turn seasonal add-ons on/off as needed  
**Condition changes:** Update time restrictions, date ranges, or dock limitations

## Organizing categories

<div class="button-container">
  <a href="https://dashboard.letsbook.app/add-ons/categories" class="button button--primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Manage categories</a>
</div>

**Reorder categories:** Drag and drop to change the order in your booking form
**Edit category names:** Update category titles and descriptions
**Layout changes:** Switch between grid, list, and detailed views per category

## Removing add-ons

Delete add-ons that are no longer offered. Add-ons with existing bookings cannot be deleted but can be marked as unavailable for future bookings.

